trans-unit.source: Do not forget that this file must be UTF-8 encoded, its fields must be separated by a comma, and the first line dedicated to field titles... Actually a standard CSV format.

trans-unit.source: To import the culture of your contacts, you must use the standard language code (ex: en, fr, br,...). This field is optional ("fr" by default).
